{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::39482209444::vessel::541e0210-f845-11f0-b3a7-d7f3241a7520","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Ionian Islands, Greece\n\nWelcome aboard the Queensland 55, a 55-foot power catamaran that redefines comfort, style, and performance on the water. Designed by the renowned Fountaine Pajot team, this flagship model is perfect for coastal cruising, extended voyages, or premium charters.\n\nWith its spacious multihull design, the Queensland 55 offers unparalleled stability and efficiency. Inside, you’ll find expansive living spaces, including a large saloon with panoramic windows, a fully equipped modern galley, and generous accommodations with ensuite cabins that feel more like a boutique hotel than a boat.\n\nFrom the moment you step onto the wide teak decks, the sense of space and luxury is undeniable. The expansive flybridge is a standout feature, offering a commanding helm station, plush sun loungers, a wet bar, and ample seating—perfect for entertaining, dining, or simply soaking in the panoramic views.\n\nInside, the Queensland 55 reveals a modern, light-filled interior with large wraparound windows that bring the sea into every moment. The saloon is beautifully appointed with a comfortable lounge area, state-of-the-art entertainment system, and a fully equipped gourmet galley that opens onto the cockpit, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience.\n\nWith 55 ft length, this spacious open yacht has the capacity for 22 guests plus captain and hostess.\n\n“Nisaki” offers all the space and amenities you need for an unforgettable time at sea.","blueprint":{"name":"NISAKI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::541e0210-f845-11f0-b3a7-d7f3241a7520::assets::f87307a0-f847-11f0-ae27-f161c2301bd4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::541e0210-f845-11f0-b3a7-d7f3241a7520::assets::f87159f0-f847-11f0-ae26-f161c2301bd4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::541e0210-f845-11f0-b3a7-d